examples.en: We had underestimated the scale of the problem.
Her talent has always been underestimated.
We underestimated how long it would take to get there.
The city underestimated the cost of the new building.
She underestimated the difficulty of saving so much money.
The firm underestimated the size of the market for their new product.
Johnson underestimated the strength of public feeling against the war.
